[
  {
    "startTime": 0.872,
    "endTime": 2.173,
    "text": "Hey, Leonard?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.173,
    "endTime": 3.66,
    "text": "Oh, hi, Penny."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.66,
    "endTime": 5.441,
    "text": "Hey, just wanted to make sure you're okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.441,
    "endTime": 7.06,
    "text": "I'm fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.06,
    "endTime": 11.584,
    "text": "I am so sorry about what happened."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.584,
    "endTime": 12.825,
    "text": "But it's not your fault."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.825,
    "endTime": 14.53,
    "text": "Yes, it is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.53,
    "endTime": 15.987,
    "text": "That's why I broke up with him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.987,
    "endTime": 17.683,
    "text": "He always does stuff like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.34,
    "endTime": 20.873,
    "text": "So, why was he at your party?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.603,
    "endTime": 36.52,
    "text": "Well, I ran into him last week, and he was just all apologetic about how he's changed, and he was just going on and on, and, and I believed him, and I'm an idiot because I always believe guys like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.43,
    "endTime": 39.489,
    "text": "And I can't go back to my party because he's there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.489,
    "endTime": 43.385,
    "text": "And I know you don't want to hear this, and I'm upset and I'm drunk and I just wanted to hug you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.582,
    "endTime": 54.27,
    "text": "There, there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.0,
    "endTime": 60.256,
    "text": "God, what is wrong with me?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.256,
    "endTime": 61.908,
    "text": "Nothing, you're perfect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.908,
    "endTime": 64.683,
    "text": "-I'm not perfect. -Yes, you are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.6,
    "endTime": 69.25,
    "text": "You really think so, don't you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.87,
    "endTime": 84.563,
    "text": "Penny?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.563,
    "endTime": 85.738,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.738,
    "endTime": 88.949,
    "text": "How much have you had to drink tonight?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.172,
    "endTime": 94.515,
    "text": "Just a lot."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.05,
    "endTime": 102.58,
    "text": "Are you sure that your being drunk and your being angry with Kurt doesn't have something to do with what's going on here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.0,
    "endTime": 105.827,
    "text": "It might."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.359,
    "endTime": 110.63,
    "text": "Boy, you're really smart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.63,
    "endTime": 112.445,
    "text": "Yeah, I'm a fricking genius."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.625,
    "endTime": 119.117,
    "text": "Leonard, you are so great."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.117,
    "endTime": 121.571,
    "text": "Why can't all guys be like you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.468,
    "endTime": 126.286,
    "text": "Because if all guys were like me, the human race couldn't survive."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.0,
    "endTime": 132.262,
    "text": "I should probably go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.262,
    "endTime": 133.903,
    "text": "Probably."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.0,
    "endTime": 144.273,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.0,
    "endTime": 156.977,
    "text": "That's right, you saw what you saw."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.696,
    "endTime": 161.594,
    "text": "That's how we roll in the Shire."
  }
]